(### Step E: Add safety and observability) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Minimum production controls:) Tj
T*
(- authentication and authorization checks) Tj
T*
(- rate limiting) Tj
T*
(- structured error handling) Tj
T*
(- audit logs and traces) Tj
T*
(- eval runs before rollout) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## 4\) Build checklist \(copy/paste\)) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(1. Define agent rules in `AGENTS.md`) Tj
T*
(2. Add or refine validator scripts) Tj
T*
(3. Add skills for recurring workflows) Tj
T*
(4. Add required MCP connectors) Tj
T*
(5. Test interactive run on one bounded task) Tj
T*
(6. Test non-interactive run on same bounded task) Tj
T*
(7. Add CI/autonomous mode only after validation is stable) Tj
T*
(8. Keep diffs small and reversible) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## 5\) Common mistakes to avoid) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(- Missing policy files, forcing behavior to depend on prompt wording) Tj
T*
(- Overly broad tasks that mix multiple objectives in one run) Tj
T*
(- Skipping validation after edits) Tj
T*
(- Letting the agent touch secrets, billing, or schema without explicit approval) Tj
T*
(- Adding many connectors before core workflow is stable) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## 6\) Suggested repo pattern) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(- `AGENTS.md` -> operational rules and constraints) Tj
T*
(- `docs/` -> runbooks and automation playbooks) Tj
T*
(- `validators/` -> deterministic quality gates) Tj
T*
(- `scripts/` -> repeatable operational commands) Tj
T*
(- `TUTORIALS/` -> onboarding docs \(this file\)) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## 7\) Practical starter prompts) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Interactive:) Tj
T*
(- "Audit the routing logic in `src/App.tsx`, propose minimal changes, then implement and run) Tj
T*
(build.") Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Non-interactive:) Tj
T*
(- `codex exec "Fix TypeScript errors in src/lib, run npm run build, and summarize changed) Tj
T*
(files."`) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## 8\) Official docs \(reference\)) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(- Tools guide: https://developers.openai.com/api/docs/guides/tools) Tj
T*
ET
